{"id":"550312ab-2119-4879-b22f-41ca7b1f7d38","name":"Tarnished Weather | G-1","description":"<p><strong>✈️ Stranded In Nowhere🐱</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dKib1PaaAe8sEr4Zgzmd8.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p></p><hr><blockquote><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 197, 170);\"><strong>🤖 Summary 💿</strong></span></h3></blockquote><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><blockquote><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 180, 88);\"><strong>Just like most of these recon patrols by now, It was initially good sailing until it wasn’t, and this was no exception to the rule by any means. The weather initially seemed to you good enough to start a patrol, despite the many warnings from the forecast and surprisingly, your higher ups went through it expecting you had everything covered. Oh buddy, did you know.</strong></span></h4><p></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 180, 88);\"><strong> That’s all I can say for what it leads you to, it would be wise to start searching for a towel, else you’ll become this Landcat’s living towel for the rest of the patrol.</strong></span></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h4></blockquote><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8mtUlQtGTzasmFc_EdvR1.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><hr><blockquote><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>🖋️ Creator's Note 🐱</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></blockquote><blockquote><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 180, 88);\"><strong>A very well deserved rework for our boy Evem (formerly known as Abrams) over here! Lowkey had fun reworking him so that I might as well end up making a new starting message soon! </strong></span></h4><p></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 180, 88);\"><strong>Anyways, hoping you guys love this new Evem \"John Landcats\" Abrams M1A2 as much as I loved having to make a new character template for him! </strong></span></h4><p></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 180, 88);\"><strong>Next on the list is Lancer as promised.</strong></span></h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></blockquote><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eGUv-nqCxUuGWOW6r2-WU.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><hr><blockquote><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>All art rights are fully owned by </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Carbine_Wolf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Karbine</strong></a><strong> and</strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/presswer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Dr. Presto</strong></a><strong>. Character owned by Dr. Karbine.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></blockquote><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Official PROJECT C.A.T.S. Website can be found here.</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KYbyXek6Sm1X6-1r6jUm2.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6Urb2j9SdxWTTo5Mvcz_F.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/G0rwUqPqGixraPg38pghS.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https: